{
  "texts": [
    "Data augmentation involves various techniques to alter the size and quality of training datasets.",
    "During training, augmentation techniques such as contrast adjustment, rotation, mirroring and brightness are utilized to increase data diversity.",
    "Due to the limited size of the Turkish sign language dataset for standalone training, different data augmentation techniques are applied to enhance the models' generalization ability on test data.",
    "With these two methods, both data size and diversity are increased.Yolov4-CSP is an object detection model based on the scaling technique [18].",
    "It can be scaled as both small and large models, with the smallest size and the least number of parameters."
  ]
}